commit 3af91040bb42c21afbb81f5568c3313125e61192
Author: Lasse Collin <lasse.collin@tukaani.org>
Date:   2014-12-20 20:42:33 +0200

    Windows: Update build instructions.

 INSTALL                     | 15 +++++++++------
 windows/INSTALL-Windows.txt | 44 +++++++++++++++++++++-----------------------
