commit eaafc4367c77ec1d910e16d11b4da293969d97a3
Author: Lasse Collin <lasse.collin@tukaani.org>
Date:   2008-06-20 16:19:54 +0300

    Remove some redundant code from LZMA encoder.

 src/liblzma/lzma/lzma_encoder.c | 15 +--------------
